Subject: RE: [T2] What year is my bus?

Or compare engine compartment air inlets and bumpers.  Larger, squared off air inlets (1972 - 1979) and rounded bumpers (1968 - 1972). So, as you can see, 1972 is the only year with this combination.

Brad Spear
'72 Westy (with high mounted turn signals)
